 team and came up with this system. These acrylic bins with adjustable dividers ended up being the perfect fit. Now our client gets to walk into a move-in ready home that is fully unpacked, beautifully organized, and ready to enjoy from day one."}, {"shortCode": "DaJtnLtOBQe", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DaJtnLtOBQe/", "caption": "Comment CLOSET & you\u2019ll automatically receive a DM with a link to these products. If you don\u2019t see a message, please let us know!\n\nWelcome home. Because you hired us, everything is already in its place.\n\nMoving doesn\u2019t have to end with weeks of living out of boxes.\n\nOur white-glove concierge move management service takes care of every detail, from decluttering and packing your current home to coordinating your move, then unpacking and professionally organizing every space in your new home.\n\nBefore you arrive, we\u2019ll even stock the essentials like toilet paper, paper towels, toothbrushes, soap, pantry staples, and other everyday necessities, so your home is truly ready to live in from day one.\n\nYou don\u2019t unpack. You don\u2019t organize. You simply walk through the door, settle in, and enjoy your new home.\n\nThat\u2019s the Organizing Spaces By Kim concierge move experience! \n\n#dallasprofessionalorganizer #ClosetOrganization #luxuryclosetorganization", "timestamp": "2026-06-29T01:43:46.000Z", "videoDuration": 31.112, "videoPlayCount": 9767, "videoViewCount": 4175, "likesCount": 75, "commentsCount": 10, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/732586460_18217275205336816_7209738870486950666_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFosUZlU85lkMugCJQztJh56NX9zwojJZ73EyruBXSUFG52uuWzD6dp-N7y1QIvs00&_nc_ohc=4Fqf0aH4js8Q7kNvwHEHo7V&_nc_gid=kjTb22hvaG6zOsCIVAgRBg&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQCxLHK-fhgkOb1tx7l9ExdMDEPOz9UWPL6FINC-A9m08Q&oe=6A619555&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-mia5-1.cdn